1. *Pištolj* je bio sakriven u fioci. (The pistol was hidden in the drawer.)
2. Pogledaj kako ovaj *pištolj* sja na suncu. (Look at how this pistol shines in the sun.)
3. Policajac je držao *pištolj* u ruci. (The policeman held a pistol in his hand.)
4. *Pistoljima* su pucali u vazduh. (They fired pistols into the air.)
5. Kupio sam novi *pištolj*. (I bought a new pistol.)
6. Borio se protiv protivnika s *pištoljem* u ruci. (He fought against the enemy with a pistol in his hand.)
7. Ovaj *pištolj* je stariji od 50 godina. (This pistol is over 50 years old.)
8. *Pištoljima* su bili opremljeni svi članovi bande. (All members of the gang were equipped with pistols.)
9. Našao sam municiju za *pištolj* u šupi. (I found ammunition for a pistol in the shed.)
10. Krivac je bio naoružan *pištoljem*. (The culprit was armed with a pistol.)